  "short_description": "MotionMuse is a powerful yet easy to use toolset for creating & editing 3D character animations. This includes animation transfer, spline based motion-editing, fast IK solver, sketching for easy posing, image overlays, curve editor and more, to help quickly and easily bring your characters to life.",
